# 📜 Flought V2: Complete Architectural & Design Change Log
# Date: 2026-03-19
# Scope: Theme Renaissance, Editor UX, and Graph Logic Removal

This document provides a line-for-line and component-by-component breakdown of the recent "Modern" theme overhaul.

---

## ── 🎨 Design System & Global Styles ──────────────────────────
### 📍 [src/app.css](file:///d:/Flought%20V2/src/app.css)
- **Constraint Overhaul**: Migrated from a property-based theme to a class-based scope (`.theme-modern-dark`).
- **New Variable Definitions**:
    - `--bg-canvas`: `#050508` (Deep night base)
    - `--bg-deep`: `#020202` (Obsidian workspace)
    - `--glass-blur`: `blur(32px) saturate(200%)`
    - `--highlight-strong`: `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14)` (Rim-lighting)
- **Global Rendering**: Added `text-rendering: optimizeLegibility` and `-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased` to the `body` tag.

---

## ── 🏗 Component Logic & Structural Modifications ──────────────

### 1. 📍 [src/components/editor/ThoughtEditor.svelte](file:///d:/Flought%20V2/src/components/editor/ThoughtEditor.svelte)
- **Layout Logic**: 
    - Added a wrapping `div` with `max-width: 800px` and `margin: 0 auto`.
    - Centered the CodeMirror instance within the viewport.
- **Typography Engine**:
    - Force-overrode `line-height` to `2.0` in the `.cm-content` class.
    - Updated the background to a 98% opaque obsidian surface to maintain font sharpness.
- **Active Line Extension**:
    - Implemented a CodeMirror state field that tracks the selection and applies a `background: var(--brand-tint-low)` to the current line.

### 2. 📍 [src/components/graph/GraphCanvas.svelte](file:///d:/Flought%20V2/src/components/graph/GraphCanvas.svelte)
- **Visualization Logic**: 
    - **DELETED**: The entire `drawHulls` function and the dependency on the `d3-hull` algorithm.
    - **MODIFIED**: The `onMount` loop now skips all grouping checks, rendering only nodes (SVG circles) and edges (SVG lines).
- **Styling**: Updated the `stroke` property of edges to use a dynamic opacity scale based on the distance between nodes.

### 3. 📍 [src/components/layout/Sidebar.svelte](file:///d:/Flought%20V2/src/components/layout/Sidebar.svelte)
- **Glass Integration**: Wrapped the navigation list in a `.glass` container with a 1px right-border.
- **Active States**: 
    - Modified the `nav` logic to apply a `box-shadow: var(--shadow-brand)` and `background: var(--brand-tint)` to the currently selected library.
- **Hover Transitions**: Reduced transition timing to `120ms` for a snappier, high-end feel.

### 4. 📍 [src/components/search/CommandPalette.svelte](file:///d:/Flought%20V2/src/components/search/CommandPalette.svelte)
- **Modal Depth**: 
    - Applied `backdrop-filter: blur(24px)` to the modal background.
    - Added an inner rim-light to the input box for better visibility against the frosted background.

